---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout
  titulo="Automatizamos tu infraestructura en la nube"
  descripcion="Ingeniero DevOps con más de 4 años diseñando infraestructuras cloud escalables en AWS, Kubernetes y Terraform."
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 text-center">
    <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-medium text-teal-700 bg-teal-50 px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-6">
      <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-teal-500"></span>
      AWS · Kubernetes · Terraform · CI/CD
    </span>
    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-medium text-gray-900 leading-tight max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-6">
      Infraestructura cloud
      <span class="text-teal-600"> escalable y automatizada</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 max-w-xl mx-auto mb-10">
      Más de 4 años diseñando, desplegando y manteniendo infraestructuras cloud altamente disponibles en AWS con Terraform, Kubernetes y pipelines CI/CD.
    </p>
    <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center flex-wrap">
      <a href="/servicios" class="bg-teal-600 text-white text-sm font-medium px-6 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-teal-700 transition-colors">Ver servicios</a>
      <a href="/contacto" class="border border-gray-200 text-gray-700 text-sm px-6 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">Contactar</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STATS -->
  <section class="border-y border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 divide-x divide-gray-100 text-center">
      <div class="px-8">
        <div class="text-3xl font-medium text-teal-600">4+</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">Años de experiencia</div>
      </div>
      <div class="px-8">
        <div class="text-3xl font-medium text-teal-600">AWS</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">Cloud principal</div>
      </div>
      <div class="px-8">
        <div class="text-3xl font-medium text-teal-600">Multi-AZ</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">Alta disponibilidad</div>
      </div>
      <div class="px-8">
        <div class="text-3xl font-medium text-teal-600">IaC</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">100% automatizado</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICIOS -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <p class="text-xs font-medium text-teal-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Servicios</p>
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4">¿Qué hacemos?</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm max-w-xl mb-12">Soluciones reales basadas en experiencia práctica con equipos de desarrollo, QA y producción.</p>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

      <!-- AWS Cloud -->
      <div class="border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-teal-200 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-md bg-teal-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-teal-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3 15a4 4 0 004 4h10a4 4 0 001-7.9A5 5 0 106 6.6" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">AWS Cloud Infrastructure</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">Diseño y gestión de infraestructuras multi-AZ altamente disponibles y tolerantes a fallos.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1">
          <span class="text-xs bg-gray-50 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">EC2</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-gray-50 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">ECS</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-gray-50 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">EKS</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-gray-50 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">RDS</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-gray-50 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">S3</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-gray-50 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">CloudFront</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-gray-50 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Route53</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- IaC -->
      <div class="border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-teal-200 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-md bg-teal-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-teal-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">Infrastructure as Code</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">Infraestructura reproducible y versionada. Entornos DEV, TEST y PROD consistentes desde el código.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1">
          <span class="text-xs bg-gray-50 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Terraform</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-gray-50 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Ansible</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-gray-50 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">VPC</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-gray-50 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">IAM</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-gray-50 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Security Groups</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CI/CD -->
      <div class="border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-teal-200 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-md bg-teal-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-teal-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">CI/CD Pipelines</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">Pipelines completamente automatizados con calidad de código integrada en cada despliegue.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1">
          <span class="text-xs bg-gray-50 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Jenkins</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-gray-50 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">GitHub Actions</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-gray-50 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">ArgoCD</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-gray-50 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Maven</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-gray-50 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">SonarQube</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Kubernetes -->
      <div class="border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-teal-200 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-md bg-teal-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-teal-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">Kubernetes & Contenedores</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">Orquestación de contenedores en producción con despliegues GitOps y gestión con Helm.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1">
          <span class="text-xs bg-gray-50 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Kubernetes</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-gray-50 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Docker</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-gray-50 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Helm</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-gray-50 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">ECR</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-gray-50 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">EKS</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Monitoreo -->
      <div class="border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-teal-200 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-md bg-teal-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-teal-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">Observabilidad & Monitoreo</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">Visibilidad total de la infraestructura con alertas proactivas y dashboards en tiempo real.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1">
          <span class="text-xs bg-gray-50 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Prometheus</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-gray-50 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Grafana</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-gray-50 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">CloudWatch</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-gray-50 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Jira</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Linux & Scripting -->
      <div class="border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-teal-200 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-md bg-teal-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-teal-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M8 9l3 3-3 3m5 0h3M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">Linux & Automatización</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">Administración de servidores Linux y automatización de tareas repetitivas con scripting.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1">
          <span class="text-xs bg-gray-50 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Ubuntu</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-gray-50 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">CentOS</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-gray-50 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Red Hat</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-gray-50 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Bash</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-gray-50 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Python</span>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- EXPERIENCIA -->
  <section class="border-t border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
      <p class="text-xs font-medium text-teal-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Experiencia</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-12">Proyectos reales</h2>
      <div class="space-y-8">

        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="w-1 bg-teal-100 rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></div>
          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">iCareMedical</span>
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 bg-gray-50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">2022 – presente</span>
              <span class="text-xs text-teal-600 bg-teal-50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Ingeniero DevOps</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Diseño e implementación de pipelines CI/CD completos en AWS con Jenkins, Maven y SonarQube. Infraestructura multi-AZ con Terraform cubriendo VPC, EC2, S3, CloudFront, RDS, Route 53 y CloudWatch. Orquestación de contenedores con Kubernetes y Helm.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="w-1 bg-gray-100 rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></div>
          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">DR Financial Services</span>
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 bg-gray-50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">2021 – 2022</span>
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 bg-gray-50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Admin. Sistemas Linux</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Administración de servidores Linux (RHEL, CentOS, Ubuntu) en entornos VMware. Automatización con scripts Bash, gestión de usuarios, permisos, LVM y resolución de incidencias.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
